title: Connect
subheading: Attendees, the best place for getting your questions answered is to join the Community Over Code Slack (aka Apachecon Slack). 
description: Community Over Code is the official conference of the Apache Software Foundation (ASF), bringing together the communities behind Apache open source projects. The event features project-specific technical tracks, real-world production use cases, and sessions on Apache governance, release management, security practices, and open source sustainability.


